## Configuration Management Patterns

### Externalized Configuration Pattern

**Avoid**: Hardcoded values in code

**Use**: Environment variables and ConfigMaps

**Quarkus application.properties**:
```properties
broker.host=${BROKER_HOST:localhost:5671}
broker.cert.db=${BROKER_CERT_DB:/secrets/ca_certificate.pem}
broker.cert.file=${BROKER_CERT_FILE:/secrets/client_certificate.pem}
broker.cert.key=${BROKER_CERT_KEY:/secrets/client_key.pem}
broker.username=${BROKER_USERNAME:swim-client}
broker.password=${BROKER_PASSWORD}

subscription-manager.url=${SM_URL:https://sm.swim.local/api/v1}
subscription-manager.username=${SM_USERNAME}
subscription-manager.password=${SM_PASSWORD}
```

**ConfigMap**:
```yaml
apiVersion: v1
kind: ConfigMap
metadata:
  name: dnotam-config
data:
  application.properties: |
    broker.host=amq-broker.swim.svc.cluster.local:5671
    subscription-manager.url=https://sm.swim.svc.cluster.local/api/v1
```

---

### Multi-Environment Pattern

**Structure**: Base + overlay configurations

**Base (base-values.yaml)**:
```yaml
replicaCount: 1
image:
  repository: dnotam-provider
  pullPolicy: IfNotPresent

resources:
  requests:
    memory: "256Mi"
    cpu: "250m"
  limits:
    memory: "512Mi"
    cpu: "500m"
```

**Development Overlay (dev-values.yaml)**:
```yaml
image:
  tag: "latest"

broker:
  host: "broker-dev.swim.local:5671"

logging:
  level: DEBUG
```

**Production Overlay (prod-values.yaml)**:
```yaml
replicaCount: 3

image:
  tag: "v1.2.3"

broker:
  host: "broker.swim.local:5671"

logging:
  level: INFO

resources:
  requests:
    memory: "512Mi"
    cpu: "500m"
  limits:
    memory: "2Gi"
    cpu: "2"
```

**Deployment**:
```bash
# Development
helm install dnotam ./chart -f base-values.yaml -f dev-values.yaml

# Production
helm install dnotam ./chart -f base-values.yaml -f prod-values.yaml
```

