## Performance Optimization Patterns

### Batching Pattern

**Problem**: High-frequency low-size messages cause overhead

**Solution**: Batch messages before publishing

**Camel Aggregator**:
```java
from("timer:generate?period=100")
  .to("bean:flightDataGenerator")
  .aggregate(constant(true), new ArrayListAggregationStrategy())
    .completionSize(100)
    .completionTimeout(5000)
  .marshal().json()
  .to("amqps://broker:5671/topic://flights.batch");
```

---

### Connection Pooling Pattern

**Problem**: Creating connections is expensive

**Solution**: Reuse connections via pooling

**Camel AMQP Connection Factory**:
```java
@Bean
public JmsConnectionFactory amqpConnectionFactory() {
    JmsConnectionFactory factory = new JmsConnectionFactory();
    factory.setRemoteURI("amqps://broker.swim.local:5671");
    factory.setUsername("swim-client");
    factory.setPassword("***");
    
    JmsPoolConnectionFactory pool = new JmsPoolConnectionFactory();
    pool.setConnectionFactory(factory);
    pool.setMaxConnections(10);
    pool.setMaxSessionsPerConnection(50);
    
    return pool;
}
```

