## Compliance Checklist

Use this checklist to verify SWIM-TI Yellow Profile compliance:

### Security
- [ ] TLS 1.2 exclusively (no SSL, TLS 1.0, TLS 1.1)
- [ ] X.509 server certificates for TLS
- [ ] Certificate validation (trust path, expiration, revocation)
- [ ] Strong cipher suites (AES-GCM, ECDHE, DHE)
- [ ] Strong passwords (min 10 chars, breach checking)
- [ ] Secure password storage (PBKDF2-SHA256, 150k iterations)
- [ ] Authentication failure logging
- [ ] Account lockout after failed attempts

### AMQP
- [ ] AMQP 1.0 protocol support
- [ ] AMQPS (AMQP over TLS)
- [ ] SASL authentication support
- [ ] Content-type header on messages
- [ ] Proper authentication method (mTLS + SASL or TLS + SASL PLAIN)

### HTTP/REST
- [ ] HTTP 1.1 support
- [ ] HTTPS (HTTP over TLS)
- [ ] Content-Type header on responses
- [ ] HTTP status codes and reason phrases
- [ ] Server authentication with X.509

### Infrastructure
- [ ] Time synchronization (NTP)
- [ ] Overload protection (rate limiting, queue limits)
- [ ] Encrypted remote admin access (SSH, HTTPS)
- [ ] Password obscuring in prompts
- [ ] Least privilege principle (non-root containers)
- [ ] Idle session termination
- [ ] Trusted software (verified checksums/signatures)
- [ ] Mandatory access control on all resources

### Operational
- [ ] Health checks (liveness, readiness)
- [ ] Metrics collection
- [ ] Audit logging
- [ ] Failed authentication logging
- [ ] Configuration externalization
- [ ] Secret management (no plaintext credentials)
